Usage
To use this project, follow these steps:

Start the server:

bash
Copy code
node server.js
The server will now be running on http://localhost:3030.

To fetch the current data, access http://localhost:3030/ from your browser or a tool like Postman.

To add new data, send a POST request to http://localhost:3030/add with the data payload.

The server automatically updates the data at defined intervals, and the changes can be observed on subsequent GET requests.

